      'Keep progress and reconstruction easy to review',
    ],
    panelLabel: 'From signal to action',
    panelSupporting: 'Not just another alert, but a clear next step with visible status, responsibility and reconstruction.',
    layers: [
      {
        label: 'Step 1',
